The Android10 devices will limit the operation of Clipboard Pro.
Unfortunately Google has removed background clipboard access for apps like Clipboard Pro in Android10.
Due to this OS specification change, Android10 devices will not save to the app clip when copying text.
When clipboard Pro is opened, it is saved to the app clip.
